Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然我已經活不久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我的犧牲能拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不害怕 我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這傢伙太強了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們快去找友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來擋住它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你一個人擋住？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還有滿開在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得向友奈道歉 帶她一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東西無雙 三好夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敬請看好我此生最大的瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹 這裡能交給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 姐姐去找友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我去把友奈帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可別出事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐 上來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就去友奈那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會開到最大戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}防護罩被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}渾蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以一個人衝太前面喔 小魚乾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起保護好 友奈要回來的這片家園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉 看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那邊是神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒完沒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全員棄艦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神樹大人在阻止我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算是神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我這次也不會退讓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路被…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉 做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼我來給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開路！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能靠精靈之力回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們回去吧 我是來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你寧可這麼做 也不肯把她交給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 我這就救你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是如果我不犧牲 世界就會滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然必須有人犧牲 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不需要你…不需要任何人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想再有好朋友被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:10:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只要忍耐就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說真心話吧 害怕就告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們既然是朋友 就向我求救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不能說 但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不想跟大家分開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們一直很拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼還要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好想 好想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}永遠和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會…為什麼非要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們不想這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我感謝神樹大人 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果要得到新世界就得犧牲別人 犧牲朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要這種新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每個人都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你真的想拯救人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再相信一次人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會繼續過人類的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 對不起 都是我說太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 我才要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對你做了好過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦 世界要毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果世界真的要毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們也無能為力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}牛鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要緊的 好溫暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們會作為人類去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者不屈 在哪裡跌倒就在哪裡站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了友奈的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有志者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社 Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者就靠毅力！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者之拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}火焰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和以前不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}牛鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}散花了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是平時的藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了友奈 身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烙印消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}於內陸山區至市區一帶發生的大規模火災
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}受災面積一週內擴大至約一萬公頃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:08.52,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由於長期避難 居民們倍感疲憊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:11.29,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要求大赦針對接下來的事 拿出合理方針
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是說 大赦早知道牆外的情況了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:16.00,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請看 本土已經化為了毫無生氣的廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人們今後只能靠著有限的資源生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:20.26,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}湧出的石油據說是神樹大人的殘骸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}孩子們是無辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}地之神消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失去庇護的人類 只能靠有限的資源活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定會發生混亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我為她們的選擇感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新時代應當是孩子們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大人要為孩子負起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是我們的天命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社變回了勇者社
